				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Additional points:
<br />
1. You don't get encumbered on horseback, even though you will still receive warnings.  I'm not sure if there's an upper limit to this, I have been encumbered to over three times my STR but still managed to gallop away from Hill Giants.
<br />

<br />
2. There is a safe fall boost.  Think I read safe fall 150 somewhere.  You can certainly avoid most minor fall damage.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=274972">Chard</a>, Arch Convoker <a href="http://www.berthall.com/">Bertoxxulous Server</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
