				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I can verify the safe fall.  Although I can't verify the skill bonus I can add that falling from the top of spiroc tree house in TD (those of you who've been there know how high it is) results in 0 dmg.
<br />

<br />
lev effects on both horse and drom are really annoying in a way you cannot go down other than waiting.  You cannot look down and move forward to progress your downward movement on a horse - you just move foward as though you weren't looking down.  
<br />

<br />
Same with looking up, you cannot prolong your desent by looking up as you could normally with lev.    So be warned.
<br />

