<br />
now i was hunting in BoT one day with my horsie. and i had to invis to go to IS. i forgot to click off horse effect. and start galping invised. and as people who are invised on a horse know, you dont see your horses head at all.  so when you click off invis you STILL dont see the head. <span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="font-style: italic"><span style="text-decoration: underline">NOTE THIS ONLY WORKS IN FIRST PERSON VIEW, IF YOU CHANGE VIEW AT ALL YOU WILL HAVE TO START ALL OVER AGAIN</span></span></span>  i found its best if you have SM1 or 2, so you dont have to recast a pet. now while your invised and on horse and cant see its head, you A) still have effect. B) you 'feel' like your still on it, IE you glap not run, and you still have the hight and fall safe C everyone eles sees that your on a horse. i just wanted to add that to help anyone.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=674042" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://users.adelphia.net/~kaseyp/images/vladasig.jpg" border="0" /></a>
